member.name: M:BeMobile.Rds.TmcEncryptionServiceKeyTable.ImportFromFile(System.String)
member.summary: Imports all service key table entries from a file. Each entry should be on a new line and each value should be separated by a comma (CSV). The table should only contain one service key (32 entries in total). For example: 'ServiceKey,EncryptionId,RotateRightValue,StartBit,XorValue', '1,15,0x05,2,0xC5'.

member.name: M:BeMobile.Rds.RdsGroup.ImportFromFile(System.String)
member.summary: Imports RDS rdsGroups represented as a hexadecimal byte string and an optional timestamp from a file. Each RDS group should be on a new line and each value should be separated by a comma (CSV). For example: 'Timestamp,BytesHexString', '2015-03-05T09:56:05,0x721005290ECD544C'.
